15:45.480 --> 15:46.400
Sang Zhi!

15:48.440 --> 15:49.480
Jiang Ming?

15:49.560 --> 15:50.560
Kenapa kau di sini?

15:51.200 --> 15:52.200
Aku mencari Sang Zhi.

15:52.760 --> 15:54.080
Aku?

15:54.600 --> 15:55.880
